description: Structured IT request intake and routing for modern teams. One routing agent triages every incoming request — hardware, software, access, or support — routes it to the right owner, tracks SLA compliance, and deflects common questions with a living FAQ. Keep ServiceNow and your ticketing system; replace the Slack noise, the Google Form black holes, and the missed SLA fire drills around them.
